    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Fuuton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You breathe out a cone of putrid, corrosive gas that deals 3d6 fire damage and 1d6 acid damage (Reflex halves). Creatures in the area are knocked back 1d4 x 5ft (Fortitude negates). This technique deals damage to unattended objects and sets fire to combustibles.</p>\n\n\n\n",
